{"submission_id":"sub_3325ebf6cb75a47c","run_id":"2026-06-21T16-32-06-699Z_2895026-1b78d851_ingest_meeting-doc-155066","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T16:46:38.317Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:3325ebf6cb75a47c8858d328635f1eb32041d0e6b71d85bce5ecd2b399104188","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_155066","observation_kind":"project","local_observation_id":"project_cbdtp_pause_oct2024","target_record_id":"project_annual-2021-cbdtp","label":"Central Business District Tolling Program - Pause Update Q2 2024","payload":{"project_name":"Central Business District Tolling Program","project_type":"tolling program","status":"paused","description":"Established by State legislation in 2019 to manage traffic congestion in Manhattan and provide $15 billion in capital funding for the MTA 2020-2024 Capital Program. Governor Hochul announced intention to pause implementation on June 5, 2024. On June 26, 2024, MTA Board adopted a resolution recognizing the pause and extending implementation until a tolling agreement among project sponsors has been executed.","document_time_status":"other","project_family":"other"},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_155066","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_155066#p025_c0012","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_155066/blocks.jsonl","page_number":25,"block_id":"p025_c0012","text_sha256":"sha256:92a4a62ea09632d287577cf9b0bcf60bc566c3b42d517637ee2ba86fd836375b","text_source":"raw_text","role":"project_description","source_quote":"The Central Business District Tolling Program (\"CBDTP\") was established by State legislation in 2019 to manage traffic congestion in Manhattan and provide $15 billion in capital funding for the MTA 2020-2024 Capital Program. On June 5, 2024, Governor Hochul announced her intention to pause the implementation of CBDTP. Subsequently, on June 26, 2024, the MTA Board adopted a resolution recognizing the pause, extending the implementation of CBDTP until a tolling agreement among the project sponsors has been executed, and authorizing the president of TBTA to implement the CBDTP after the tolling agreement has been executed."}]},"validation":{"state":"rejected","issues":["evidence_refs[0].source_quote must be 280 characters or fewer"]}}
